'''柏保路·馬里'''（Pablo Marí Villar，{{IPA-es|ˈpaβlo maˈɾi biˈʎaɾ}}，{{bd|1993年|8月31日||}}），是一名[[西班牙|西班牙]]職業足球員，司職[[中後衛|中後衛]]。目前由[[英格蘭超級足球聯賽|英格蘭超級足球聯賽]]球會[[阿仙奴足球會|阿仙奴]]外借至[[義甲|義甲]]球會[[乌迪内斯足球俱乐部|乌迪内斯]]。

== 球會 ==
=== 曼城 ===
2016年8月15日，馬里轉會至[[英格蘭超級足球聯賽|英格蘭超級足球聯賽]]球會[[曼徹斯特城足球會|曼城]]，1日後被外借至[[吉罗纳足球俱乐部|基羅納]]，為期1個賽季<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gironafc.cat/es/noticia/el-central-pablo-mari-llega-al-girona|title=El central Pablo Marí llega al Girona|trans-title=Stopper Pablo Marí arrives at Girona|publisher=Girona FC|language=es|date=2016-08-16|accessdate=2016-08-16|archive-date=2017-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170510190549/http://www.gironafc.cat/es/noticia/el-central-pablo-mari-llega-al-girona|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

於其後2年間，馬里分別外借至[[荷兰足球甲级联赛|荷兰足球甲级联赛]]球會[[NAC比達|NAC比達]]<ref>{{cite news|url=https://as.com/futbol/2017/11/16/internacional/1510836284_487384.html|title=Pablo Marí brilla en el NAC Breda e interesa en la Premier|trans-title=Pablo Marí shines at NAC Breda and catches the Premier's eye|newspaper=Diario AS|first=Víctor|last=López|language=es|date=2017-11-16|accessdate=2018-07-19|archive-date=2020-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201110135123/https://as.com/futbol/2017/11/16/internacional/1510836284_487384.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mancity.com/news/first-team/first-team-news/2017/november/man-city-loan-watch-27-november|title=Loan watch: Cup joy for Roberts’ Celtic|publisher=Manchester City F.C.|date=2017-11-27|accessdate=2018-07-19|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201015024028/https://www.mancity.com/news/first-team/first-team-news/2017/november/man-city-loan-watch-27-november|dead-url=no}}</ref>和[[西班牙乙組足球聯賽|西班牙乙組足球聯賽]]球會[[拉科鲁尼亚体育俱乐部|拉科鲁尼亚]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rcdeportivo.es/noticia/pablo-mari-nuevo-jugador-del-deportivo|title=Pablo Marí, nuevo jugador del Deportivo|trans-title=Pablo Marí, new Deportivo player|publisher=Deportivo La Coruña|language=es|date=2018-07-01|accessdate=2018-07-01|archive-date=2021-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201230908/https://www.rcdeportivo.es/noticia/pablo-mari-nuevo-jugador-del-deportivo|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他於效力NAC比達期間成為球隊的隊長。
=== 法林明高 ===
2019年7月11日，馬里轉會至[[巴西足球甲級聯賽|巴西足球甲級聯賽]]球會[[法林明高競賽會|法林明高]]，簽約至2022年<ref>{{cite tweet|number=1149302112842653698|title=Tem novidade no Mengão. O zagueiro espanhol Pablo Marí, de 25 anos, é o nosso novo reforço. Ele foi comprado junto ao Manchester City e assinou contrato com o Mais Querido até dezembro de 2022. Seja bem-vindo! Muito sucesso com o Manto Sagrado! 🔴⚫️ #CRF|trans-title=News at Mengão. Spanish stopper Pablo Marí, aged 25, is our new addition. He was acquired from Manchester City and signed a contract with The Dearest until December 2022. Welcome! All the best at the Holy Cloak! 🔴⚫️ #CRF|author-link=Flamengo|user=Flamengo|language=pt|date= 2019-07-11|accessdate= 2019-07-11}}</ref>，轉會費為130萬歐元<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.espn.com.br/futebol/artigo/_/id/5825971/flamengo-pablo-mari-chega-por-r-55-milhoes-e-apos-jorge-jesus-desaprovar-zapata|title=Pablo Marí chega por R$5,5 milhões e após Jorge Jesus desaprovar Zapata|trans-title=Pablo Marí arrives for R$5,5 million and after Jorge Jesus says no to Zapata|website=ESPN Brasil|language=pt|date=2019-07-11|accessdate=2019-08-30|archive-date=2019-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190714165026/https://www.espn.com.br/futebol/artigo/_/id/5825971/flamengo-pablo-mari-chega-por-r-55-milhoes-e-apos-jorge-jesus-desaprovar-zapata|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他成為第3位效力該球會的西班牙球員<ref>{{cite web|url=https://jovempan.uol.com.br/esportes/futebol/quem-e-pablo-mari-terceiro-espanhol-da-historia-do-flamengo-veja-lances-do-zagueiro.html|title=Quem é Pablo Marí, terceiro espanhol da história do Flamengo; veja lances do zagueiro|trans-title=Who is Pablo Marí, third Spaniard in the history of Flamengo; see stopper in action|publisher=Jovem Pan|language=pt|date=2019-07-11|accessdate=2019-08-30|archive-date=2019-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190714165329/https://jovempan.uol.com.br/esportes/futebol/quem-e-pablo-mari-terceiro-espanhol-da-historia-do-flamengo-veja-lances-do-zagueiro.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。7月28日，馬里於聯賽客勝[[保地花高足球競賽會|保地花高]]3比2的比賽中首次代表球隊上陣<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cbf.com.br/futebol-brasileiro/competicoes/campeonato-brasileiro-serie-a/2019/116|title=De virada, Flamengo vence clássico com o Botafogo pelo Brasileirão|trans-title=In comeback style, Flamengo win classic with Botafogo for the ''Brasileirão''|publisher=Brazilian Football Confederation|language=pt|date=2019-07-28|accessdate=2019-10-18|archive-date=2020-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930060140/https://www.cbf.com.br/futebol-brasileiro/competicoes/campeonato-brasileiro-serie-a/2019/116|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他迅速融入球隊一隊，與[[洛迪高·卡爾奧|-{zh-hans:罗德里戈·卡约;zh-hk:洛迪高·卡爾奧;zh-tw:羅德里格·卡約;}-]]組成正選防線<ref>{{cite web|url=https://globoesporte.globo.com/futebol/times/flamengo/noticia/espanhol-incansavel-com-mais-de-24h-de-futebol-pablo-mari-puxa-fila-em-maratona-do-flamengo-por-doblete.ghtml|title=Espanhol incansável: com mais de 24h de futebol, Pablo Marí puxa fila em maratona do Flamengo|trans-title=Tireless Spaniard: with more than 24h of football, Pablo Marí pulls rank in Flamengo marathon|publisher=Globo Esporte|first=Cahê|last=Mota|language=pt|date=2019-10-18|accessdate=2019-10-19|archive-date=2019-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191211025454/https://globoesporte.globo.com/futebol/times/flamengo/noticia/espanhol-incansavel-com-mais-de-24h-de-futebol-pablo-mari-puxa-fila-em-maratona-do-flamengo-por-doblete.ghtml|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。

2019年8月25日，馬里於客勝[[塞阿拉竞技俱乐部|施亞拉]]3比0的比賽中，於禁區內以窩利攻入射進轉會後首個入球<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.regiaonline.com/flamengo-vence-ceara-com-gol-de-bicicleta-de-arrascaeta-e-vira-lider/|title=Flamengo vence Ceará com gol de bicicleta de Arrascaeta e vira líder|trans-title=Flamengo beat Ceará with bicycle kick from Arrascaeta and are now leaders|publisher=Região Online|language=pt|date=2019-08-25|accessdate=2019-11-23|archive-date=2019-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191216162508/http://www.regiaonline.com/flamengo-vence-ceara-com-gol-de-bicicleta-de-arrascaeta-e-vira-lider/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。9月7日，他在對陣[[阿瓦伊足球俱乐部|艾華爾]]時，以頭鎚攻入1球，協助球隊作客以3比0勝出<ref>{{cite web|url=https://globoesporte.globo.com/sc/futebol/brasileirao-serie-a/jogo/07-09-2019/avai-flamengo.ghtml|title=Com primeiro gol de Reinier e mais um de Gabriel, Flamengo vence o Avaí por 3 a 0 no Mané Garrincha|trans-title=With first goal from Reinier and another one from Gabriel, Flamengo beat Avaí 3 to 0 at the Mané Garrincha|publisher=Globo Esporte|language=pt|date=2019-09-07|accessdate=2019-12-09|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129074337/https://globoesporte.globo.com/sc/futebol/brasileirao-serie-a/jogo/07-09-2019/avai-flamengo.ghtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。11月，馬里隨球隊贏得[[南美解放者杯|南美解放者杯]]冠軍，成為首位捧盃的西班牙人<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.marca.com/en/football/international-football/2019/11/24/5dda5f3fca4741ce0c8b464f.html|title=Pablo Mari becomes the first Spaniard to win the Copa Libertadores|newspaper=Marca|location=Spain|first=Dan|last=Rowell|date=2019-11-24|accessdate=2019-12-09|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201230121130/https://www.marca.com/en/football/international-football/2019/11/24/5dda5f3fca4741ce0c8b464f.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==== 阿仙奴（外借）====
2020年1月29日，馬里被外借至[[英格蘭超級足球聯賽|英格蘭超級足球聯賽]]球會[[阿仙奴足球會|阿仙奴]]，直至賽季完結<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.arsenal.com/news/pablo-mari-join-club-loan|title=Pablo Mari to join the club on loan|publisher=Arsenal F.C.|date=2020-01-29|accessdate=2020-01-29|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115150757/https://www.arsenal.com/news/pablo-mari-join-club-loan|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==== 阿仙奴 ====
2020年7月，[[阿仙奴足球會|阿仙奴]]正式買斷馬里。

2020年12月3日，馬里在[[歐足總歐洲聯賽|歐足總歐洲聯賽]]中以4比1擊敗[[維也納迅速體育會|維也納迅速]]的比賽中踢進了自己的第一個進球。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/55154336 |title=Arsenal 4-1 Rapid Vienna: Gunners win in Europa League in front of 2,000 fans |website=BBC Sport |date=2020-12-03 |accessdate=2020-12-04 |archive-date=2020-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201207115617/https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/55154336 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

